{"title": "News", "html": "<section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_medium\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-grid type_grid layout_blog_classic\" id=\"us_grid_1\"><style id=\"us_grid_1_css\">#us_grid_1 .w-grid-item:not(:last-child){margin-bottom:5rem}#us_grid_1 .g-loadmore{margin-top:5rem}</style><style>.layout_blog_classic .w-grid-item-h{}.layout_blog_classic .usg_post_image_1{margin-bottom:1rem!important}.layout_blog_classic .usg_post_title_1{font-size:1.4rem!important;margin-bottom:0.5rem!important}.layout_blog_classic .usg_hwrapper_1{color:#999999!important;font-size:0.9rem!important}.layout_blog_classic .usg_post_content_1{margin-top:0.5rem!important}.layout_blog_classic .usg_btn_1{margin-top:1.5rem!important}</style><div class=\"w-grid-list\"><article class=\"w-grid-item size_1x1 post-8425 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news tag-action tag-diagnostic tag-gef tag-guinea tag-international-union-for-the-conservation-of-nature tag-iucn tag-liberia tag-makona tag-mano-river-basin tag-mano-river-union tag-national-water-resources-management-agency tag-plan tag-relationship tag-strategic tag-transboundary\" data-id=\"8425\">\n\n\t<div class=\"w-grid-item-h\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-post-elm post_image usg_post_image_1 stretched\"><a href=\"/mru-gef-project-outlines-plans-to-protect-biodiversity-and-water-resources/\" aria-label=\"MRU-GEF Project Outlines Plans to Protect Biodiversity and Water Resources\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2023/01/IMG_7225-1024x683.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2023/01/IMG_7225-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2023/01/IMG_7225-300x200.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2023/01/IMG_7225-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2023/01/IMG_7225-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></div><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/mru-gef-project-outlines-plans-to-protect-biodiversity-and-water-resources/\">MRU-GEF Project Outlines Plans to Protect Biodiversity and Water Resources</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2023-01-23T16:13:28+00:00\"><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i>January 23, 2023</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_author usg_post_author_1 color_link_inherit vcard author\"><i class=\"far fa-user\"></i><div class=\"post-author-meta\"><a class=\"post-author-name fn\" href=\"/author/johnterry/\">John Terry</a></a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_taxonomy usg_post_taxonomy_1 style_simple color_link_inherit\"><i class=\"far fa-folder-open\"></i><a href=\"/category/news/\">News</a></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments usg_post_comments_1 layout_amount color_link_inherit with_word\"><i class=\"far fa-comments\"></i><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/mru-gef-project-outlines-plans-to-protect-biodiversity-and-water-resources/#respond\">No Comments</a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content usg_post_content_1\">The Mano River Union Ecosystem Conservation and International Water Resources Management project on Monday started a three-day meeting in Kenema city to develop its Strategic Action Plan (SAP) in order&hellip;</div><a class=\"w-btn us-btn-style_2 usg_btn_1\" href=\"/mru-gef-project-outlines-plans-to-protect-biodiversity-and-water-resources/\"><span class=\"w-btn-label\">Read More</span></a>\t</div>\n\n</article>\n\n<article class=\"w-grid-item size_1x1 post-8399 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news tag-acc tag-compliance tag-national-water-resources-management-agency tag-nwrma-regulation tag-parliament-certifies tag-partnership tag-sierra-leone-police tag-slp tag-water-regulations\" data-id=\"8399\">\n\n\t<div class=\"w-grid-item-h\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-post-elm post_image usg_post_image_1 stretched\"><a href=\"/forming-the-right-alliances-for-enforcement/\" aria-label=\"Forming The Right Alliances for Enforcement\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/11/IMG_5972-1024x683.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/11/IMG_5972-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/11/IMG_5972-300x200.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/11/IMG_5972-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/11/IMG_5972-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></div><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/forming-the-right-alliances-for-enforcement/\">Forming The Right Alliances for Enforcement</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2022-11-14T09:44:42+00:00\"><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i>November 14, 2022</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_author usg_post_author_1 color_link_inherit vcard author\"><i class=\"far fa-user\"></i><div class=\"post-author-meta\"><a class=\"post-author-name fn\" href=\"/author/johnterry/\">John Terry</a></a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_taxonomy usg_post_taxonomy_1 style_simple color_link_inherit\"><i class=\"far fa-folder-open\"></i><a href=\"/category/news/\">News</a></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments usg_post_comments_1 layout_amount color_link_inherit with_word\"><i class=\"far fa-comments\"></i><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/forming-the-right-alliances-for-enforcement/#respond\">No Comments</a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content usg_post_content_1\">The Parliament of Sierra Leone passed into law the National Water Resources Management Agency Act in 2017, which established the National Water Resources Management Agency with broad mandates to protect,&hellip;</div><a class=\"w-btn us-btn-style_2 usg_btn_1\" href=\"/forming-the-right-alliances-for-enforcement/\"><span class=\"w-btn-label\">Read More</span></a>\t</div>\n\n</article>\n\n<article class=\"w-grid-item size_1x1 post-8385 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news tag-acc tag-corruption tag-partnership tag-sandi\" data-id=\"8385\">\n\n\t<div class=\"w-grid-item-h\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-post-elm post_image usg_post_image_1 stretched\"><a href=\"/it-is-a-corruption-offence-to-breach-the-water-resources-mgt-law/\" aria-label=\"It Is a Corruption Offence to Breach the Water Resources Mgt. Law.\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/10/IMG_6036-1024x683.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/10/IMG_6036-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/10/IMG_6036-300x200.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/10/IMG_6036-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/10/IMG_6036-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></div><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/it-is-a-corruption-offence-to-breach-the-water-resources-mgt-law/\">It Is a Corruption Offence to Breach the Water Resources Mgt. Law.</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2022-10-27T16:27:58+00:00\"><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i>October 27, 2022</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_author usg_post_author_1 color_link_inherit vcard author\"><i class=\"far fa-user\"></i><div class=\"post-author-meta\"><a class=\"post-author-name fn\" href=\"/author/johnterry/\">John Terry</a></a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_taxonomy usg_post_taxonomy_1 style_simple color_link_inherit\"><i class=\"far fa-folder-open\"></i><a href=\"/category/news/\">News</a></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments usg_post_comments_1 layout_amount color_link_inherit with_word\"><i class=\"far fa-comments\"></i><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/it-is-a-corruption-offence-to-breach-the-water-resources-mgt-law/#respond\">No Comments</a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content usg_post_content_1\">Freetown, October 27th-The National Water Resources Management Agency (NWRMA) has today signed a memorandum of understanding (MoU) with the Anti-Corruption Commission (ACC) at the Commission’s headquarters in Freetown. The agreement&hellip;</div><a class=\"w-btn us-btn-style_2 usg_btn_1\" href=\"/it-is-a-corruption-offence-to-breach-the-water-resources-mgt-law/\"><span class=\"w-btn-label\">Read More</span></a>\t</div>\n\n</article>\n\n<article class=\"w-grid-item size_1x1 post-8378 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news\" data-id=\"8378\">\n\n\t<div class=\"w-grid-item-h\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-post-elm post_image usg_post_image_1 stretched\"><a href=\"/nwrma-partners-with-police-to-protect-water-resources/\" aria-label=\"NWRMA Partners With Police to Protect Water Resources\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/10/IMG_5992-1024x683.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/10/IMG_5992-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/10/IMG_5992-300x200.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/10/IMG_5992-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/10/IMG_5992-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></div><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/nwrma-partners-with-police-to-protect-water-resources/\">NWRMA Partners With Police to Protect Water Resources</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2022-10-13T14:11:16+00:00\"><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i>October 13, 2022</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_author usg_post_author_1 color_link_inherit vcard author\"><i class=\"far fa-user\"></i><div class=\"post-author-meta\"><a class=\"post-author-name fn\" href=\"/author/johnterry/\">John Terry</a></a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_taxonomy usg_post_taxonomy_1 style_simple color_link_inherit\"><i class=\"far fa-folder-open\"></i><a href=\"/category/news/\">News</a></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments usg_post_comments_1 layout_amount color_link_inherit with_word\"><i class=\"far fa-comments\"></i><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/nwrma-partners-with-police-to-protect-water-resources/#respond\">No Comments</a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content usg_post_content_1\">The National Water Resources Management Agency (NWRMA) has today signed a memorandum of understanding (MoU) with the Sierra Leone Police (SLP) at the Police headquarters in Freetown. The agreement sets&hellip;</div><a class=\"w-btn us-btn-style_2 usg_btn_1\" href=\"/nwrma-partners-with-police-to-protect-water-resources/\"><span class=\"w-btn-label\">Read More</span></a>\t</div>\n\n</article>\n\n<article class=\"w-grid-item size_1x1 post-8368 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-frontpage category-news category-regulation category-report tag-fourth-estate tag-media tag-national-water-resources-management-agency tag-nwrma-regulation tag-relationship tag-water-regulations tag-water-resources tag-workshop\" data-id=\"8368\">\n\n\t<div class=\"w-grid-item-h\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-post-elm post_image usg_post_image_1 stretched\"><a href=\"/nwrma-engages-the-media-on-regulations/\" aria-label=\"NWRMA Engages the Media on Regulations\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/482B242C-0345-4F3F-8E88-AB4D11881130.png-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/482B242C-0345-4F3F-8E88-AB4D11881130.png-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/482B242C-0345-4F3F-8E88-AB4D11881130.png-300x169.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/482B242C-0345-4F3F-8E88-AB4D11881130.png.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></div><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/nwrma-engages-the-media-on-regulations/\">NWRMA Engages the Media on Regulations</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2022-08-26T10:41:58+00:00\"><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i>August 26, 2022</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_author usg_post_author_1 color_link_inherit vcard author\"><i class=\"far fa-user\"></i><div class=\"post-author-meta\"><a class=\"post-author-name fn\" href=\"/author/johnterry/\">John Terry</a></a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_taxonomy usg_post_taxonomy_1 style_simple color_link_inherit\"><i class=\"far fa-folder-open\"></i><a href=\"/category/news/frontpage/\">Frontpage</a>, <a href=\"/category/news/\">News</a>, <a href=\"/category/regulation/\">Regulation</a>, <a href=\"/category/report/\">Report</a></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments usg_post_comments_1 layout_amount color_link_inherit with_word\"><i class=\"far fa-comments\"></i><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/nwrma-engages-the-media-on-regulations/#respond\">No Comments</a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content usg_post_content_1\">The National Water Resources Management Agency (NWRMA) has on Friday 26th August 2022 conducted a training workshop for media practitioners on the Rules and Procedures for Compliance with the National&hellip;</div><a class=\"w-btn us-btn-style_2 usg_btn_1\" href=\"/nwrma-engages-the-media-on-regulations/\"><span class=\"w-btn-label\">Read More</span></a>\t</div>\n\n</article>\n\n<article class=\"w-grid-item size_1x1 post-8371 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-frontpage category-news tag-automatic-water-station tag-staff-gauge\" data-id=\"8371\">\n\n\t<div class=\"w-grid-item-h\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-post-elm post_image usg_post_image_1 stretched\"><a href=\"/data-collectors-who-volunteer-protect-sierra-leones-rivers/\" aria-label=\"Data Collectors Who Volunteer To Protect Sierra Leone’s Rivers\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/IMG_5107-1024x683.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/IMG_5107-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/IMG_5107-300x200.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/IMG_5107-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/IMG_5107-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></div><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/data-collectors-who-volunteer-protect-sierra-leones-rivers/\">Data Collectors Who Volunteer To Protect Sierra Leone’s Rivers</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2022-08-25T10:51:23+00:00\"><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i>August 25, 2022</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_author usg_post_author_1 color_link_inherit vcard author\"><i class=\"far fa-user\"></i><div class=\"post-author-meta\"><a class=\"post-author-name fn\" href=\"/author/johnterry/\">John Terry</a></a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_taxonomy usg_post_taxonomy_1 style_simple color_link_inherit\"><i class=\"far fa-folder-open\"></i><a href=\"/category/news/frontpage/\">Frontpage</a>, <a href=\"/category/news/\">News</a></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments usg_post_comments_1 layout_amount color_link_inherit with_word\"><i class=\"far fa-comments\"></i><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/data-collectors-who-volunteer-protect-sierra-leones-rivers/#respond\">No Comments</a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content usg_post_content_1\">Data is very critical to protect, regulate, and manage Sierra Leone’s water Resources. Correct data inform as to where the high tides are, and what the characteristics have been like&hellip;</div><a class=\"w-btn us-btn-style_2 usg_btn_1\" href=\"/data-collectors-who-volunteer-protect-sierra-leones-rivers/\"><span class=\"w-btn-label\">Read More</span></a>\t</div>\n\n</article>\n\n<article class=\"w-grid-item size_1x1 post-8286 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-frontpage category-news tag-nwrma-regulation tag-parliament-certifies tag-water-regulations\" data-id=\"8286\">\n\n\t<div class=\"w-grid-item-h\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-post-elm post_image usg_post_image_1 stretched\"><a href=\"/parliament-certifies-four-water-regulations/\" aria-label=\"Parliament Certifies Four Water Regulations\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/08/Four-Water-Regulations.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/08/Four-Water-Regulations.png 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/08/Four-Water-Regulations-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></div><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/parliament-certifies-four-water-regulations/\">Parliament Certifies Four Water Regulations</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2022-08-14T09:35:14+00:00\"><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i>August 14, 2022</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_author usg_post_author_1 color_link_inherit vcard author\"><i class=\"far fa-user\"></i><div class=\"post-author-meta\"><a class=\"post-author-name fn\" href=\"/author/johnterry/\">John Terry</a></a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_taxonomy usg_post_taxonomy_1 style_simple color_link_inherit\"><i class=\"far fa-folder-open\"></i><a href=\"/category/news/frontpage/\">Frontpage</a>, <a href=\"/category/news/\">News</a></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments usg_post_comments_1 layout_amount color_link_inherit with_word\"><i class=\"far fa-comments\"></i><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/parliament-certifies-four-water-regulations/#respond\">No Comments</a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content usg_post_content_1\">An Act of Parliament established the National Water Resources Management Agency (NWRMA) in 2017. The Agency is responsible for managing and protecting water resources, granting water rights to competing users,&hellip;</div><a class=\"w-btn us-btn-style_2 usg_btn_1\" href=\"/parliament-certifies-four-water-regulations/\"><span class=\"w-btn-label\">Read More</span></a>\t</div>\n\n</article>\n\n<article class=\"w-grid-item size_1x1 post-8361 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news\" data-id=\"8361\">\n\n\t<div class=\"w-grid-item-h\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-post-elm post_image usg_post_image_1 stretched\"><a href=\"/how-drama-is-raising-the-consciousness-around-water-resources-management/\" aria-label=\"How Drama Is Raising the Consciousness Around Water Resources Management\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"565\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/Drama1-1024x565.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/Drama1-1024x565.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/Drama1-300x166.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/Drama1-1536x848.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/09/Drama1.jpg 1554w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></div><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/how-drama-is-raising-the-consciousness-around-water-resources-management/\">How Drama Is Raising the Consciousness Around Water Resources Management</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2022-08-05T10:20:37+00:00\"><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i>August 5, 2022</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_author usg_post_author_1 color_link_inherit vcard author\"><i class=\"far fa-user\"></i><div class=\"post-author-meta\"><a class=\"post-author-name fn\" href=\"/author/johnterry/\">John Terry</a></a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_taxonomy usg_post_taxonomy_1 style_simple color_link_inherit\"><i class=\"far fa-folder-open\"></i><a href=\"/category/news/\">News</a></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments usg_post_comments_1 layout_amount color_link_inherit with_word\"><i class=\"far fa-comments\"></i><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/how-drama-is-raising-the-consciousness-around-water-resources-management/#respond\">No Comments</a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content usg_post_content_1\">When people hear the sound of the African drum, they stop in their tracks. It goes by a lot of names around Sierra Leone, but the two most prominent are&hellip;</div><a class=\"w-btn us-btn-style_2 usg_btn_1\" href=\"/how-drama-is-raising-the-consciousness-around-water-resources-management/\"><span class=\"w-btn-label\">Read More</span></a>\t</div>\n\n</article>\n\n<article class=\"w-grid-item size_1x1 post-8210 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news\" data-id=\"8210\">\n\n\t<div class=\"w-grid-item-h\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-post-elm post_image usg_post_image_1 stretched\"><a href=\"/soldiers-receive-bikes-for-forest-protection/\" aria-label=\"Soldiers Receive Bikes for Forest Protection\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/08/IMG_4023-1024x683.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/08/IMG_4023-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/08/IMG_4023-300x200.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/08/IMG_4023-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/08/IMG_4023-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></div><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/soldiers-receive-bikes-for-forest-protection/\">Soldiers Receive Bikes for Forest Protection</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2022-07-28T14:50:29+00:00\"><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i>July 28, 2022</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_author usg_post_author_1 color_link_inherit vcard author\"><i class=\"far fa-user\"></i><div class=\"post-author-meta\"><a class=\"post-author-name fn\" href=\"/author/johnterry/\">John Terry</a></a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_taxonomy usg_post_taxonomy_1 style_simple color_link_inherit\"><i class=\"far fa-folder-open\"></i><a href=\"/category/news/\">News</a></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments usg_post_comments_1 layout_amount color_link_inherit with_word\"><i class=\"far fa-comments\"></i><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/soldiers-receive-bikes-for-forest-protection/#respond\">No Comments</a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content usg_post_content_1\">Freetown, July 28-The National Water Resources Management Agency (NWRMA) in collaboration with Catholic Relief Services in Sierra Leone (CRS) and The Nature Conservancy have today handed over ten (10) motorcycles&hellip;</div><a class=\"w-btn us-btn-style_2 usg_btn_1\" href=\"/soldiers-receive-bikes-for-forest-protection/\"><span class=\"w-btn-label\">Read More</span></a>\t</div>\n\n</article>\n\n<article class=\"w-grid-item size_1x1 post-8221 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news\" data-id=\"8221\">\n\n\t<div class=\"w-grid-item-h\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-post-elm post_image usg_post_image_1 stretched\"><a href=\"/groundwater-monitoring-goes-digital/\" aria-label=\"Groundwater Monitoring Goes Digital\"><img width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2022/07/Ground-Water-Relief-7-768x1024.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a></div><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/groundwater-monitoring-goes-digital/\">Groundwater Monitoring Goes Digital</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2022-07-24T16:03:34+00:00\"><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i>July 24, 2022</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_aut